"  6 to 8 medium potatoes (about 3 pounds), peeled and cut into 1-inch cubes","1/2 pound bacon, cooked and crumbled","6  green onions, chopped","2  celery ribs, finely chopped","2 tablespoons diced pimiento, drained","3/4 teaspoon salt","1/4 teaspoon pepper","1/2 cup mayonnaise","1/2 cup sour cream","  Garnishes: paprika, celery sticks"